"drivers present in Linux Mint by default."
msgstr "有些显卡和主板在 Linux Mint 中默认的开源驱动下并不能良好工作。"

#: ../../boot_options.rst:7
msgid "Compatibility mode"
msgstr "兼容模式"

#: ../../boot_options.rst:9
msgid ""
"The easiest option is to select ``compatibility mode`` from the USB stick "
"(or DVD) boot menu."
msgstr "最简单的选项是在U盘或 DVD 的启动菜单中选择 ``compatibility mode``。"

